content: Welcome to your new project! I can help you edit it however you want. What would you like to do?

I want to generate a game that allows the user to accumulate points based on the times clicked, so if i click 10 times, i get 10 points. For that, I need to send it as event to a smart contract and let the smart contract keep track of the points. Points have to be accumulative, so if i send 30 more later, in total there are 40.
Conversation switched to smart_contract_assistant. Adopt the persona of smart_contract_assistant immediately.
